room_title: Escape room "Mission Improbable" by Sprightly Escapes in Denver
room_description:
Scientists have recently created the first-ever time machine. You and your group have been selected to travel back to prehistoric times to try and save dinosaurs from extinction. However, if you do not complete your mission within 60 minutes, you will be trapped with the dinosaurs... forever.
Room is located upstairs with very limited seating and lighting.
